        <p class="tagline">Mission Control for Self-Hosters & Indie Devs</p>
        <p class="description">
          Manage SSH connections, Docker containers, Coolify deployments and Git releases from one unified interface.
        </p>
        <div class="cta">
          <a href="#quickstart" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</a>
          <a href="https://github.com/Degi100/pctrl" class="btn btn-secondary">View on GitHub</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="quickstart" class="quickstart">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Quick Start</h2>
        <div class="code-block">
          <pre><code># Install from source
git clone https://github.com/Degi100/pctrl.git
cd pctrl
cargo install --path apps/cli

# Run pctrl
pctrl              # Shows styled status banner
pctrl --help       # List all commands
pctrl -m tui       # Terminal UI mode</code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="features" class="features">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Features</h2>
        <div class="feature-grid">
          <div class="feature">
            <h3>üîê SSH Management</h3>
            <p>Add, remove, connect and execute commands on remote servers with SSH key authentication.</p>
            <code>pctrl ssh add "Server" 10.0.0.1 -u root</code>
          </div>
          <div class="feature">
            <h3>üê≥ Docker Control</h3>
            <p>Manage Docker hosts and containers across multiple machines. List, start, and stop containers.</p>
            <code>pctrl docker add "Local" -u unix:///var/run/docker.sock</code>
          </div>
          <div class="feature">
            <h3>üöÄ Coolify Integration</h3>
            <p>Deploy and monitor applications on your Coolify instances with API token authentication.</p>
            <code>pctrl coolify add "Prod" -u https://coolify.io -t token</code>
          </div>
          <div class="feature">
            <h3>üì¶ Git Releases</h3>
            <p>Create tags and manage releases for your Git repositories. Push tags to remotes.</p>
            <code>pctrl git add "Project" -p /path/to/repo</code>
          </div>
          <div class="feature">
            <h3>üíª Three Modes</h3>
            <p>Choose your interface: CLI for scripting, TUI for terminal dashboards, GUI for desktop apps.</p>
            <code>pctrl -m tui | pctrl -m gui</code>
          </div>
          <div class="feature">
            <h3>üîí Encrypted Storage</h3>
            <p>AES-256-GCM encrypted SQLite database with Argon2 key derivation. Your data stays secure.</p>
            <code>~/.local/share/pctrl/pctrl.db</code>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="modes" class="modes">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Three Ways to Control</h2>
        <div class="mode-grid">
          <div class="mode">
            <h3>CLI Mode</h3>
            <p>Fast, scriptable command-line interface with full CRUD operations for all resources.</p>
            <div class="status complete">‚úÖ Complete</div>
          </div>
          <div class="mode">
            <h3>TUI Mode</h3>
            <p>Beautiful terminal dashboard with keyboard navigation using ratatui.</p>
            <div class="status complete">‚úÖ Complete</div>
          </div>
          <div class="mode">
            <h3>GUI Mode</h3>
            <p>Desktop application built with Tauri and React for a native experience.</p>
            <div class="status progress">üîÑ In Progress</div>
          </div>
